{"tid":790633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"空姐就梁頌昕行李事件覆核同行同檢規定獲判勝訴","createTime":"2018-08-23T07:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T02:42:09.000Z","uid":51271,"like":224,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"d383673cc960976df63d6db437f53eb5e8b24ef9","tid":790633,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:17:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1414097-20180823.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1414097-20180823.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=rHqTbPGR3zbQL8maV%2FRfIAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=016ff762\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1414097-20180823.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=54a1abea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1414097-20180823.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"59081c005b6527b90b0641a9a89ea7bfbd76f4f4","tid":790633,"uid":64275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc83141eb8e66151759313f5537a67dc0edf779b","tid":790633,"uid":5489,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:21:22.000Z","msg":"收皮啦余若海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620cea848913e6b50d7485cd021290c0f782e71e","tid":790633,"uid":48083,"like":96,"dislike":1,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:21:59.000Z","msg":"前特首梁振英的幼女梁頌昕，前年3月底遺留行李在機場禁區外，其後獲機管局准許，由航空公司職員代她攜同行李通過安檢帶進禁區，毋須「同行同檢」；港龍機艙服務員不滿機管局決定，申請司法覆核，高等法院今頒下判辭，裁定機艙服務員勝訴，法庭並要求機管局支付訟費。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180823/s00001/1535008174998?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180823%2Fs00001%2F1535008174998%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=rHqTbPGR3zbQL8maV%2FRfIAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=0ef7f273\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180823%2Fs00001%2F1535008174998%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=b3649f3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180823/s00001/1535008174998?web_push=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac5fe36da9557966aaf96506dff8878c1daa60a","tid":790633,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c1e792f7d0a98d27249dd4ef6ea851ec406efb","tid":790633,"uid":29874,"like":125,"dislike":1,"score":124,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:26:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180823&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58596471\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180823%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58596471&d=rHqTbPGR3zbQL8maV%2FRfIAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=1c54e8d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180823%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58596471&h=816fce8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180823&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58596471</a><br />\n【行李門】指機管局違「同行同檢」做法 空姐司法覆核勝訴<br />\n<br />\n前特首梁振英前年疑向機場員工施壓，迫令國泰職員「特事特辦」代送其幼女梁頌昕的手提行李進入禁區的「行李門」事件，機管局事後提交報告堅稱沒違保安程序，引來空姐不滿此舉有違旅客及行李需「同行同檢」的一貫做法。空姐早前提出司法覆核，機管局及後在案件開審前兩個月刪條文欲避官司，法官今午頒下判詞，裁定空姐勝訴，機管局須支付申請人訟費。<br />\n<br />\n根據《香港航空保安計劃》（ASP）條文6.2.10「所有針對隨身行李的檢查，一概應在乘客在場下進行」，即包括首檢（X光檢查）以及覆檢（人手搜查），但機管局在本年4月將有關條文刪除，並加入新6.2.11條「所有針對覆檢的檢查，一概應在乘客在場下進行」。換言之在新規定下，僅要求乘客在需要人手抽檢的覆檢時在場，至於採用X光機檢查的首次檢查時應否在場則不再有明文規定。機管局於審訊時解釋，此舉是為了節省法庭的時間和訟費開支，認為本案只淪為學術討論。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：HCAL117/16】<br />\n<br />\n直頭改埋保安條文來就單案，真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08901dd72be187618422a6c042e9444c52fd8fb4","tid":790633,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3359521f8689c7156fa7747e0a91e1237a3fb32","tid":790633,"uid":37612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:27:21.000Z","msg":"機管局會唔會上訴"},{"pid":"81068cd7b8557ab23df306616eabaa2a3d5e2774","tid":790633,"uid":6063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:27:29.000Z","msg":"只有違反修定前的保安計劃<br />\n<br />\n姐係點？"},{"pid":"1dfd1200cce46a3a12ef509337feb4391b2373d2","tid":790633,"uid":39628,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:28:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直頭改埋保安條文來就單案，真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港共隻手遮天有咩做唔出<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efc349095de13cd6056c8e4f435938dd8677427","tid":790633,"uid":42921,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:28:56.000Z","msg":"勝訴有乜用？"},{"pid":"5f02edace7c2075b54225406e739d2a3a5759197","tid":790633,"uid":31841,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:28:59.000Z","msg":"叫689屈隻空姐港獨咪得囉"},{"pid":"467d5028b7e29a55171351788933399e1e7704e2","tid":790633,"uid":163801,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"08c1e792f7d0a98d27249dd4ef6ea851ec406efb","tid":790633,"uid":29874,"like":125,"dislike":1,"score":124,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:26:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180823&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58596471\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180823%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58596471&d=rHqTbPGR3zbQL8maV%2FRfIAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMj